rComments: Prof Dunbar is just amazing. I took his creativity and reasoning course as a d level psych. Initially, I chose it because it had space but boy was I glad I did choose this one.  no midterms or finals but there were assignments and a final research experiment write-up. Fun teacher always ready to clarify doubts!
This course especially the 2nd half had a large amount of reading but if you read before classes, everything makes sense.
